Habitualize

Build better habits with
intelligent context

Habitualize goes beyond yes/no tracking. It understands why habits succeed or fail, connects patterns across your life, and gives you AI-powered insights to improve — consistently and sustainably.

See Habitualize in action

User Guide

Everything you need to know to master Habitualize and build lasting habits.

1. Create Your First Habit

Tap the “+” button and name your habit clearly — for example “Morning Meditation”.

2. Set Your Schedule

Choose specific days or a custom frequency that fits your life.

3. Add Context

Track mood, energy, or location to uncover what truly affects consistency.

Daily Check-ins

Log completion along with short notes — what helped or blocked you.

  • Time of day
  • Energy level
  • Mood
  • Location
  • People around

Weekly Analysis

AI finds patterns — sleep, weekdays, environments — and explains what works best for you.

Ask Anything

  • Why am I missing mornings?
  • Best workout time?
  • How to stay consistent on weekends?
Pro Tips

✨ Start small — 2–3 habits beat 10 abandoned ones.

📝 Be honest — missed days are insights, not failures.

🎯 Be specific — clarity drives consistency.
